summary: 20 Photographs Scattered Around the Sanctum 1. A young woman, young and wild-haired, cooing at a swaddled infant with wispy...
body:
20 Photographs Scattered Around the Sanctum

1. A young woman, young and wild-haired, cooing at a swaddled infant with wispy raven hair and mystic blue-green eyes.

2. Peter and Shuri smiling, tranquil Wakandan fields behind them, trademark Tony Stark sunglasses on their noses.

3. Tony slumped over a lab table, his face buried in his grease-stained arm. 

4. Stephen and Christine at a banquet. Proof that tailored tuxes and smooth, undamaged hands were real. 

5. Peter passed out in a webbed hammock at the Compound, a half-read textbook dangling dangerously from his limp fingers.

6. Thor holding a roasted turkey triumphantly above his head while Natasha bats Tony’s hands away from the spread of various pies. 

7. Two shadowy figures, one tall and the other small, embracing from a distance.  

8. Wong glaring darkly at Tony, a single roast beef sandwich sitting between them. 

9. The training courtyard at Kamar-Taj at sunrise. The auburn leaves striking brightly against the tangerine sky. 

10. Tony, tears running down the tired panels of his bleeding face, clutching a relived Peter.

11. Stephen and Wong standing proudly in front of the New York Sanctum, the sides of Stephen’s face still marred by the damage inflicted by Dormammu.

12. A flock of butterflies flitting around Tony, whose eyes sparkle as he stares at something out of frame. 

13. The Guardians, reunited, waving from the cockpit of Quill’s ship. 

14. The Avengers, old and new, smiling as they huddle together in front of the reclaimed Avengers Tower. To the side, hidden in the mighty shadow of Thor, two figures – one tall, one small – try to hide their interwoven fingers behind a maroon cloak. 

15. May Parker smiling blissfully as Peter scowls down at his matching ugly Christmas sweater.

16. Stephen’s head, bowed in sleep, resting on the top of Tony’s head as Rhodey snickers from the other end of the couch.

17. Bruce grinning sheepishly as Thor coos at the ebony rabbit being held out to him. 

18. A line of men and women, dressed in black, standing solemnly on a raised platform as Maria Hill points from the podium at the large canvas of Nick Fury. 

19. Tony smiling brightly with an arm slung over a suit of Iron Man armor. His face is less lined, his hair less grey. 

20. Dozens of figures, all dressed elegantly in fine cut suits and flowing gowns, tossing rice at two retreating figures – one tall, one small.
